Adblock Plus - Wikipedia





















 






Adblock Plus

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search

Not to be confused with AdBlock.

Adblock Plus





Preferences dialog box of Adblock Plus showing a group of filters



