^ "Detailed changelog for Adblock Plus 0.7.5.2". Adblockplus.org. Retrieved November 4, 2011. 
^ "How To Bypass Websites that Block "AdBlock" (e.g. Forbes)". Brandon, Nick. Retrieved July 14, 2015. 
^ "Intro to Chrome addons hacking: fingerprinting". The World. According to Koto. 2012-02-17. Retrieved 2016-06-22. Webpages can sometimes interact with Chrome addons and that might be dangerous, more on that later. Meanwhile, a warmup - trick to detect addons you have installed. 
^ "Google Chrome Extensions: Migrate to Manifest V2". Google. Retrieved February 11, 2013. 
^ "Adblock Plus 1.3 for Google Chrome™ released". Adblockplus.org. Retrieved February 11, 2013. 


