		Going above and beyond high standards.	

	Products

		Our extensive range of meat products includes both fresh and frozen beef, lamb, sausages and burgers, satisfying a wide range of commercial requirements.	

Across our entire portfolio, from fresh sirloin steaks to frozen beef burgers, it’s our goal to deliver optimum quality and efficiency – delivering products that meet and exceed both the commercial expectations of our retailers and quality expectations of our end consumers.

Our OneVision strategy is about delivering food processes and products that meet the requirements of our customers. We have a team dedicated to product development. This enables us to create something new to match every type of outlet and to drive cost efficient innovation throughout our range.


















											New product development is just one example of our OneVision commercial strategy in practice.									




													We’re dedicated to ensuring the full traceability of our products.											






















About ABP Food Group | Meat processing | Ireland UK Europe | ABP Food Group





























